== What is Hub Culture? ==

Hub is an invitation-based social network with locations all over the world and its own currency called "Ven".

It is an example of a [[phyles|phyle]] that has a shared identity and multiple locations around the world called Pavilions<ref>[https://hubculture.com/pavilions/ List of Hub Culture Pavilions]</ref>.

